Image 14 of 14 Dyal, Tivy overwhelm Boerne Champion in third quarter 1 / 14 Back to Gallery KERRVILLE — Given a look at the final score, one might find it difficult to believe Kerrville Tivy trailed by 12 points midway though the second quarter of its showdown against Boerne Champion.
Thanks to a 35-point third quarter, Tivy erased any doubt about the outcome of Friday night’s District 27-5A contest as it pulled away for a wild 65-49 victory at Antler Stadium.
